ws%2Fparachute-economist-raghuram-rajan-under-fire-for-remarks-on-india-growth-5325652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20RBI%20governor%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20India's%20growth%20and%20saying%20that%20there%20are%20significant%20structural%20problems%20that%20need%20to%20be%20fixed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fparachute-economist-raghuram-rajan-under-fire-for-remarks-on-india-growth-5325652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lawyers%20Write%20To%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20Claim%20Group%20Trying%20To%20%26quot%3BPressure%26quot%3B%20Judiciary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20lawyers%2C%20including%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%20and%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India%20chairperson%20Manan%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20alleging%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bvested%20interest%20group%26quot%3B%20is%20trying%20to%20pressure%20the%20judiciary%20and%20defame%20courts%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20basis%20of%20frivolous%20logic%20and%20stale%20political%20agendas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20pressure%20tactics%20are%20most%20obvious%20in%20political%20cases%2C%20particularly%20those%20involving%20political%20figures%20accused%20of%20corruption.%20These%20tactics%20are%20damaging%20to%20our%20courts%20and%20threaten%20our%20democratic%20fabric%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20letter%2C%20dated%20March%2026%2C%20addressed%20to%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20shared%20by%20official%20sources%2C%20targeted%20a%20section%20of%20lawyers%20without%20naming%20them%20and%20alleged%20that%20they%20defend%20politicians%20by%20the%20day%20and%20then%20try%20to%20influence%20judges%20through%20the%20media%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20interest%20group%20creates%20false%20narratives%20of%20a%20supposed%20better%20past%20and%20golden%20period%20of%20courts%2C%20contrasting%20it%20with%20the%20happenings%20in%20the%20present%2C%20the%20letter%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20comments%20are%20aimed%20at%20influencing%20courts%20and%20embarrassing%20them%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20of%20lawyers%2C%20who%20are%20behind%20the%20letter%20titled%20%26quot%3BJudiciary%20Under%20Threat-Safeguarding%20Judiciary%20from%20Political%20and%20Professional%20Pressure%26quot%3B%2C%20number%20around%20600%20and%20also%20include%20Adish%20Aggarwala%2C%20Chetan%20Mittal%2C%20Pinky%20Anand%2C%20Hitesh%20Jain%2C%20Ujjwala%20Pawar%2C%20Uday%20Holla%20and%20Swarupama%20Chaturvedi%2C%20the%20official%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20lawyers%20behind%20the%20letter%20have%20mentioned%20no%20specific%20cases%2C%20the%20development%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20courts%20are%20dealing%20with%20several%20high-profile%20criminal%20cases%20of%20corruption%20involving%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20central%20government%20of%20targeting%20their%20leaders%20as%20part%20of%20its%20political%20vendetta%2C%20a%20charge%20refuted%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20These%20parties%2C%20whose%20ranks%20include%20some%20noted%20lawyers%2C%20have%20joined%20hands%20against%20the%20recent%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy-linked%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20critics%2C%20these%20lawyers%20have%20accused%20them%20of%20suggesting%20that%20courts%20in%20the%20past%20were%20easier%20to%20influence.%20This%20shakes%20the%20public's%20trust%20in%20courts%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20antics%20are%20vitiating%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20trust%20and%20harmony%2C%20which%20characterises%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20their%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20concocted%20an%20entire%20theory%20of%20%26quot%3Bbench%20fixing%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20not%20just%20disrespectful%20and%20contemptuous%20but%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20honour%20and%20dignity%20of%20courts%2C%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20also%20stooped%20to%20the%20level%20of%20comparing%20our%20courts%20to%20those%20countries%20where%20there%20is%20no%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20accusing%20our%20judicial%20institutions%20with%20unfair%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20critics%20have%20adopted%20the%20%26quot%3Bmy%20way%20or%20the%20highway%26quot%3B%20approach%20at%20work%20as%20they%20hail%20the%20decisions%20they%20agree%20with%2C%20but%20any%20decision%20they%20disagree%20with%2C%20is%20trashed%2C%20smeared%20and%20disregarded%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20two-faced%20behaviour%20is%20harmful%20to%20the%20respect%20a%20common%20man%20should%20have%20for%20our%20legal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said%20and%20claimed%20that%20this%20cherry%20picking%20has%20been%20visible%20in%20very%20recent%20judgments%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20elements%20are%20trying%20to%20influence%20who%20the%20judges%20are%20in%20their%20cases%20and%20spread%20lies%20on%20social%20media%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20them%20to%20decide%20in%20a%20particular%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20alleged%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20timing%2C%20the%20lawyers%20said%20it%20is%20all%20happening%20when%20the%20country%20is%20headed%20for%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20reminded%20of%20similar%20antics%20in%202018-2019%20when%20they%20took%20to%20their%20'hit%20and%20run'%20activities%2C%20including%20fabricating%20wrong%20narratives.%20These%20efforts%20to%20belittle%20and%20manipulate%20the%20courts%20for%20personal%20and%20political%20reasons%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20stand%20strong%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20protect%20courts%20from%20these%20alleged%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStaying%20silent%20or%20doing%20nothing%20could%20accidentally%20give%20more%20power%20to%20those%20who%20mean%20to%20do%20harm.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20maintain%20dignified%20silence%20as%20such%20efforts%20are%20happening%20since%20few%20years%20and%20too%20frequently%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20CJI's%20leadership%20is%20crucial%20in%20these%20%26quot%3Btough%20times%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711606380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjlc3in08_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_18_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawyers-write-to-chief-justice-of-india-claim-vested-interest-group-trying-to-pressure-judiciary-5325536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20lawyers%2C%20including%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%20and%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India%20chairperson%20Manan%20Mishra%2C%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20alleging%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bvested%20interest%20group%26quot%3B%20is%20trying%20to%20pressure%20the%20judiciary%20and%20defame%20courts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawyers-write-to-chief-justice-of-india-claim-vested-interest-group-trying-to-pressure-judiciary-5325536%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Human%20Brains%20Getting%20Bigger%2C%20And%20It's%20Good%20News%20For%20Some%3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20size%20of%20human%20brain%20is%20increasing%2C%20a%20new%20study%20has%20revealed.%20It%20added%20that%20this%20gradual%20increase%20could%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia%20in%20younger%20generations.%20The%20research%2C%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamaneurology%2Ffullarticle%2F2816798%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJAMA%20Neurology%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20based%20on%20the%20image%20analysis%20of%20more%20than%203%2C000%20participants%20in%20the%20US%20who%20were%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2055%20and%2065.%20The%20team%20from%20University%20of%20California%20(UC)%20Davis%20Health%20concluded%20that%20those%20born%20in%20the%201970s%20(Generation%20X)%20have%20a%206.6%20per%20cent%20greater%20overall%20brain%20volume%20than%20those%20born%20in%20the%201930s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20Generation%20X%20has%208%20per%20cent%20greater%20volume%20of%20white%20matter%20and%2015%20per%20cent%20more%20gray%20matter%20than%20the%20member%20of%20the%20previous%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hippocampus%2C%20which%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20memory%20in%20learning%2C%20expanded%20by%205.7%20per%20cent%20in%20volume%20compared%20to%20previous%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20was%20perceptible%20even%20after%20considering%20other%20factors%20like%20height%2C%20age%20and%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20was%20led%20by%20Charles%20DeCarli%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%20Davis%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20decade%20someone%20is%20born%20appears%20to%20impact%20brain%20size%20and%20potentially%20long-term%20brain%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenetics%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20determining%20brain%20size%2C%20but%20our%20findings%20indicate%20external%20influences%20-%20such%20as%20health%2C%20social%2C%20cultural%20and%20educational%20factors%20-%20may%20also%20play%20a%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencealert.com%2Fyounger-generations-have-larger-brains-is-that-healthier%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScience%20Alert%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researcher%20said%20the%20increased%20size%20of%20the%20brain%20will%20lead%20to%20increased%20reserve%20against%20the%20diseases%20of%20aging%2C%20%26quot%3Bconsequently%20reducing%20overall%20risk%20of%20dementia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disease%20affects%20millions%20of%20people%20across%20the%20world%2C%20especially%20due%20to%20increase%20in%20ageing%20population%20in%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20study%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20line%20with%20the%20recent%20trends%20that%20show%20incidence%20of%20dementia%20decreasing%20in%20every%20decade.%20The%20risk%20of%20disease%20is%20also%20considerably%20low%20in%20younger%20generations%20because%20of%20their%20healthier%20lifestyles%20and%20upbringing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711606380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F9lq1qdao_brain-scan-generic-unsplash_625x300_30_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhuman-brains-getting-bigger-and-its-good-news-for-some-study-5325648%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20study%20also%20found%20that%20Generation%20X%20has%208%20per%20cent%20greater%20volume%20of%20white%20matter%20and%2015%20per%20cent%20more%20gray%20matter%20than%20the%20member%20of%20the%20previous%20generation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhuman-brains-getting-bigger-and-its-good-news-for-some-study-5325648%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20container%20ship%20gets%20named%20after%20G-Dragon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711606285000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstat