cted-social-media-parenting-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paris%20Hilton%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20influencer%20culture%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Btoxic%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20want%20her%20kids%20to%20be%20caught%20up%20in%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-hilton-kids-addicted-social-media-parenting-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20HC%20rejects%20Congress%20plea%20in%20tax%20probe%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711605427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108839841%2Cimgsize-1831589.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi-high-court-dismisses-congress-plea-challenging-income-tax-probe%2Farticleshow%2F108839714.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20More%20Multiple%20Exams%20For%20PhD%20Admissions%2C%20UGC%20Makes%20NET%20Scores%20Mandatory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20move%20aimed%20at%20streamlining%20the%20process%20of%20PhD%20admissions%2C%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20has%20declared%20that%20scores%20obtained%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(NET)%20will%20be%20accepted%20starting%20academic%20session%202024-25.%20This%20decision%20comes%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20students%20who%20previously%20had%20to%20go%20through%20multiple%20entrance%20exams%20conducted%20by%20various%20universities%20for%20PhD%20admissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20recommendations%20from%20an%20expert%20committee%2C%20the%20university%20body%20made%20this%20decision%20in%20the%20578th%20meeting%20held%20on%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NET%2C%20conducted%20biannually%20in%20June%20and%20December%2C%20serves%20the%20dual%20purpose%20of%20awarding%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowships%20(JRF)%20and%20selecting%20Assistant%20Professors%20among%20master's%20degree%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnder%20the%20new%20directive%2C%20from%20June%202024%20onwards%2C%20UGC%20NET%20qualified%20candidates%20will%20now%20be%20eligible%20for%20PhD%20admissions%20in%20three%20categories%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdmission%20to%20PhD%20with%20JRF%20and%20appointment%20as%20assistant%20Professor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdmission%20to%20PhD%20without%20JRF%20and%20appointment%20as%20assistant%20professor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdmission%20to%20PhD%20programme%20only%20and%20not%20for%20the%20award%20of%20JRF%20or%20appointment%20as%20assistant%20professor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUGC%20chairman%20Mamidala%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20academic%20session%202024-2025%2C%20all%20universities%20can%20use%20NET%20scores%20for%20admission%20to%20PhD%20programmes%2C%20replacing%20the%20need%20for%20separate%20entrance%20tests%20conducted%20by%20individual%20universities%20or%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20(HEIs)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNTA%20is%20working%20on%20launching%20the%20NET%20application%20process%20for%20the%20June%202024%20session%20sometime%20next%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20academic%20session%202024-2025%2C%20all%20universities%20can%20use%20NET%20score%20for%20admission%20to%20PhD%20programmes%20in%20place%20of%20entrance%20tests%20conducted%20by%20the%20different%20universities%2FHEIs.%20NTA%20is%20working%20on%20launching%20the%20NET%20application%20process%20for%20June%202024%20session%20sometime%20next%20week.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIVzKgu56gB%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIVzKgu56gB%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mamidala%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20(%40mamidala90)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmamidala90%2Fstatus%2F1773049893122130262%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NET%20result%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20percentile%20along%20with%20the%20marks%20obtained%20by%20each%20candidate%2C%20facilitating%20their%20use%20for%20PhD%20admission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(Minimum%20Standards%20and%20Procedures%20for%20Award%20of%20PhD%20Degree)%20Regulations%2C%202022%2C%20candidates%20who%20qualify%20for%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20(JRF)%20undergo%20an%20interview%20for%20admission%20into%20PhD%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20students%20falling%20under%20Categories%202%20and%203%2C%20PhD%20admissions%20will%20consider%2070%20per%20cent%20weightage%20for%20test%20scores%20and%2030%20per%20cent%20weightage%20for%20the%20interview.%20Admission%20to%20PhD%20programmes%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20combined%20merit%20of%20NET%20marks%20and%20interview%2Fviva%20voce%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENET%20marks%20obtained%20by%20candidates%20in%20Categories%202%20and%203%20will%20remain%20valid%20for%20one%20year%20for%20PhD%20admissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JRF-qualified%20students%20are%20admitted%20into%20the%20PhD%20programme%20based%20on%20an%20interview%20as%20per%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(Minimum%20Standards%20and%20Procedures%20for%20Award%20of%20PhD%20Degree)%20Regulations%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20students%20qualifying%20under%20Categories%202%20and%203%2C%2070%20per%20cent%20weightage%20will%20be%20assigned%20to%20test%20scores%2C%20while%2030%20per%20cent%20will%20be%20allocated%20to%20the%20interview%20for%20PhD%20admission.%20The%20admission%20process%20will%20be%20determined%20b