C%20%26quot%3BHow%20is%20India's%20cooperation%20shaping%20up%20on%20the%20assassination%20investigations%20of%20Canadian%20citizen%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20when%20Canada%20has%20credible%20allegations%20and%20India%20expects%20Canada%20to%20complete%20its%20own%20investigation%20first%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20PM%20responded%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20is%20something%20that%20we%20all%20should%20take%20extremely%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20credible%20allegations%20that%20agents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20were%20involved%20in--that%20is%20something%20that%20we%20did%20not%20declare%20lightly%2C%20but%20our%20responsibility%20to%20protect%20all%20Canadians%20from%20illegal%20actions%20by%20foreign%20governments%20is%20something%20that%2C%20as%20a%20country%20grounded%20in%20diversity%2C%20we%20need%20to%20take%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20earlier%20denied%20the%20charges%20as%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau%20said%20the%20Canadian%20government%20is%20ensuring%20appropriate%20probe%20is%20being%20done%2C%20according%20to%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20the%20CPAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20have%20been%20unequivocal%20about%20standing%20up%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20appropriate%20investigations%20are%20being%20done%20in%20full%20accordance%20with%20our%20justice%20system%20and%20our%20police%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Canadian%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20said%20they%20are%20working%20constructively%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20working.%20We're%20looking%20to%20work%20constructively%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20this%20could%20have%20happened%2C%20and%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20no%20Canadians%20are%20ever%20vulnerable%20again%20to%20foreign%20interference%20by%20any%20international%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20as%20he%20came%20out%20of%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20had%20alleged%20the%20Indian%20government's%20role%20in%20Nijjar's%20killing%2C%20a%20charge%20that%20India%20rejected%20and%20led%20to%20the%20deterioration%20of%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20motivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20Canada%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20present%20any%20evidence%20to%20back%20its%20claims%20over%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711598640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7aio8c8o_justin-trudeau-reuters_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flooking-to-work-constructively-with-indian-govt-canadian-pm-on-nijjars-killing-5323537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20on%20Thursday%20said%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20work%20constructively%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20killing%20of%20designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Floo