tent%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711597336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108836104%2Cimgsize-903154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhunter-bidens-lawyers-push-california-judge-to-toss-out-tax-charges%2Farticleshow%2F108836029.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108836029.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhunter-bidens-lawyers-push-california-judge-to-toss-out-tax-charges%2Farticleshow%2F108836029.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhunter-bidens-lawyers-push-california-judge-to-toss-out-tax-charges%2Famp_articleshow%2F108836029.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhunter-bidens-lawyers-push-california-judge-to-toss-out-tax-charges%2Famp_articleshow%2F108836029.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vehicles%20Stuck%20Under%20US%20Bridge%20Debris%20But%20Efforts%20To%20Find%20More%20Bodies%20End%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20of%20the%20cargo%20freighter%20that%20knocked%20down%20a%20highway%20bridge%20into%20Baltimore%20Harbor%20had%20radioed%20for%20tugboat%20help%20and%20reported%20a%20power%20loss%20minutes%20earlier%2C%20federal%20safety%20officials%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20citing%20audio%20from%20the%20ship's%20%26quot%3Bblack%20box%26quot%3B%20data%20recorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20also%20said%20that%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%2C%20a%20traffic%20artery%20over%20the%20harbor%20built%20in%201976%2C%20lacked%20structural%20engineering%20redundancies%20common%20to%20newer%20spans%2C%20making%20it%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20a%20catastrophic%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20insights%20into%20the%20fatal%20disaster%20emerged%20a%20day%20after%20the%20massive%20Singapore-flagged%20container%20ship%20Dali%20sailing%20out%20of%20Baltimore%20Harbor%20bound%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%20reported%20losing%20power%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20maneuver%20before%20plowing%20into%20a%20support%20pylon%20of%20the%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20brought%20most%20of%20the%20bridge%20tumbling%20into%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20Patapsco%20River%20almost%20immediately%2C%20blocking%20shipping%20lanes%20and%20forcing%20the%20indefinite%20closure%20of%20the%20Port%20of%20Baltimore%2C%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20on%20the%20U.S.%20Eastern%20Seaboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivers%20on%20Wednesday%20recovered%20the%20remains%20of%20two%20of%20the%20six%20workers%20missing%20since%20the%20crumbling%20bridge%20tossed%20them%20into%20the%20water%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaryland%20State%20Police%20Colonel%20Roland%20Butler%20said%20a%20red%20pickup%20truck%20containing%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20two%20men%20was%20found%20in%20about%2025%20feet%20(7.62%20m)%20of%20water%20near%20the%20mid-section%20of%20the%20fallen%20bridge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20authorities%20had%20suspended%20efforts%20to%20retrieve%20more%20bodies%20from%20the%20depths%20due%20to%20increasingly%20treacherous%20conditions%20in%20the%20wreckage-strewn%20harbor.%20Butler%20said%20sonar%20images%20showed%20additional%20submerged%20vehicles%20%26quot%3Bencased%26quot%3B%20in%20sunken%20bridge%20debris%2C%20making%20them%20difficult%20to%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20men%20whose%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20on%20Wednesday%20were%20identified%20as%20Alejandro%20Hernandez%20Fuentes%2C%2035%2C%20of%20Baltimore%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Dorlian%20Ronial%20Castillo%20Cabrera%2C%2026%2C%20of%20nearby%20Dundalk%2C%20originally%20from%20Guatemala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20more%20workers%20who%20were%20part%20of%20a%20crew%20filling%20potholes%20on%20the%20bridge's%20road%20surface%20remained%20missing%20and%20presumed%20dead.%20The%20six%20also%20included%20immigrants%20from%20Honduras%20and%20El%20Salvador%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescuers%20pulled%20two%20workers%20from%20the%20water%20alive%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20one%20was%20hospitalized.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20fallout%20could%20be%20staggering.%20The%20port%20handles%20more%20automobile%20and%20farm%20equipment%20freight%20than%20any%20other%20in%20the%20country%2C%20as%20well%20as%20container%20freight%20and%20bulk%20goods%20ranging%20from%20sugar%20to%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Pete%20Buttigieg%20said%20the%208%2C000%20jobs%20are%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20associated%26quot%3B%20with%20port%20operations%2C%20which%20generate%20%242%20million%20a%20day%20in%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20economists%20and%20logistics%20experts%20doubted%20the%20port%20closure%20would%20trigger%20a%20major%20U.S.%20supply%20chain%20crisis%20or%20significant%20spike%20in%20the%20price%20of%20goods%2C%20due%20to%20ample%20capacity%20at%20rival%20shipping%20hubs%20along%20the%20East%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%2C%20which%20occurred%20at%201%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20has%20created%20a%20traffic%20quagmire%20as%20well%20for%20Baltimore%20and%20the%20surrounding%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EINTERVIEWING%20SURVIVORS%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%20an%20NTSB%20team%20boarded%20the%20idled%20freighter%2C%20still%20anchored%20in%20the%20harbor%20channel%20with%20part%20of%20the%20mangled%20bridge%20splayed%20over%20its%20bow%2C%20to%20begin%20interviewing%20the%20ship's%20two%20pilots%20and%2021%20regular%20crew%20members%20who%20remained%20on%20the%20vessel%2C%20safety%20board%20chief%20Jennifer%20Homendy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20also%20began%20reviewing%20information%20collected%20from%20the%20ship's%20Voyage%20Data%20Recorder%2C%20including%20radio%20traffic%20between%20the%20pilot%20and%20shore-based%20authorities%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20was%20heard%20calling%20for%20tugboat%20assistance%20several%20minutes%20before%20the%20crash%2C%20the%20first%20indication%20of%20distress%20to%20harbor%20officials%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20radio%20report%20that%20the%20ship%20had%20lost%20all%20power%20and%20was%20approaching%20the%20bridge%2C%20NTSB%20officials%20said%20at%20a%20news%20briefing%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideo%20footage%20that%20captured%20the%20accident%20show%20the%20ship's%20lights%20winking%20off%2C%20then%20back%20on%20briefly%20before%20the%20vessel's%20lights%20go%20out%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHomendy%20said%20recorder%20data%20was%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20with%20a%20power%20outage%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20an%20actual%20blackout%20had%20yet%20to%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recorder%20also%20picked%20up%20commands%20to%20the%20crew%20to%20drop%20anchor%2C%20presumably%20aimed%20at%20slowing%20the%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafety%20board%20investigator%20Marcel%20Muise%20said%20data%20showed%20the%20Dali%2C%20measuring%20about%20three%20football%20fields%20in%20length%20and%20piled%20high%20with%20shipping%20containers%2C%20was%20moving%20at%20about%208%20miles%20per%20hour%20(12.8%20km)%20when%20it%20struck%20a%20bridge%20abutment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHomendy%20noted%20that%20the%20bridge%2C%20while%20deemed%20to%20be%20in%20%26quot%3Bsatisfactory%26quot%3B%20condition%20from%20its%20most%20recent%20inspection%20in%202023%2C%20was%20constructed%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20failure%20of%20one%20structural%20member%20%26quot%3Bwould%20likely%20cause%20a%20portion%20of%2C%20or%20the%20entire%20bridge%20to%20collapse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20details%20of%20last-minute%20efforts%20to%20save%20lives%20emerged%20on%20Wednesday%20from%20open-source%20recordings%20of%20emergency%20radio%20chatter%20from%20the%20moments%20that%20authorities%20were%20alerted%20that%20the%20cargo%20ship%20Dali%20was%20drifting%20out%20of%20control%20toward%20Key%20Bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHold%20all%20traffic%20on%20the%20Key%20Bridge.%20There's%20a%20ship%20approaching%20that%20just%20lost%20their%20steering%2C%26quot%3B%20someone%20is%20heard%20saying%20over%20a%20police%20radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20voices%20were%20heard%20discussing%20next%20steps%2C%20including%20alerting%20any%20work%20crews%20to%20leave%20the%20bridge%2C%20one%20broke%20through%20to%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20bridge%20just%20fell%20down!%26quot%3B%20The%20audio%20was%20carried%20by%20the%20public%20streaming%20service%20Broadcastify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20Coast%20Guard's%20first%20priorities%20are%20to%20restore%20the%20waterway%20for%20shipping%2C%20stabilize%20the%20crippled%20vessel%20and%20extricate%20it%2C%20Vice%20Admiral%20Peter%20Gautier%20said%20at%20a%20White%20House%20news%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20ship's%204%2C700%20cargo%20containers%2C%2056%20hold%20hazardous%20materials%20but%20there%20is%20no%20threat%20to%20the%20public%2C%20Gautier%20said.%20Two%20containers%20went%20overboard%20during%20the%20crash%20but%20they%20did%20not%20contain%20hazardous%20materials.%20The%20ship%20was%20carrying%20more%20than%201.5%20million%20gallons%20of%20fuel%20oil%2C%20Gautier%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHomendy%20said%20some%20of%20hazmat%20containers%20aboard%20the%20vessel%20had%20been%20breached%20and%20a%20sheen%20was%20noticed%20on%20the%20water's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711597080000%2C%22visual%22%3