ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fskura-style-announces-eva-mendes-as-new-co-owner-and-brand-ambassador-301540317.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eco-owner%20and%20brand%20ambassador%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20cleaning%20product%20company%2C%20Skura%20Style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMeeting%20in%20the%20middle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMendes%20and%20Gosling's%20approach%20to%20childcare%20isn't%20one%20that%20can%20be%20well%20replicated%20among%20ordinary%20couples%2C%20Mu%20Zheng%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20department%20of%20sociology%20and%20anthropology%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20it's%20very%20likely%20Eva%20Mendes%20and%20Ryan%20Gosling%20reached%20the%20agreement%20based%20on%20a%20fair%2C%20egalitarian%20discussion%20and%20decision-making%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20more%20regular%20scenarios%2C%20it%20may%20be%20a%20very%20gendered%20situation%20where%20women%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20make%20such%20a%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20for%20couples%20to%20navigate%20childcare%20arrangements%20is%20to%20be%20open%20to%20discussion%20and%20make%20decisions%20on%20an%20equal%20standing%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEva%20and%20Ryan%20seem%20to%20have%20an%20amazing%20connection%2C%20and%20their%20intuition%20may%20have%20been%20aligned%20on%20how%20to%20raise%20their%20family%2C%20hence%20why%20they%20were%20able%20to%20have%20the%20'non-verbal%20agreement%2C'%26quot%3B%20relationship%20coach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famiethedatingcoach.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmie%20Leadingham%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20not%20all%20couples%20naturally%20have%20this%20type%20of%20connection%2C%20and%20being%20communicative%20about%20their%20needs%20can%20help%20create%20clarity%20and%20a%20structure%20that%20makes%20both%20people%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20for%20partners%20to%20discuss%20the%20arrangement%20with%20each%20other%20so%20that%20they%20know%20they're%20both%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20This%20can%20help%20avoid%20resentment%2C%20Leadingham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEvery%20couple%20is%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20everyone%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20like%20Mendes%20and%20Gosling%2C%20and%20have%20one%20partner%20focus%20almost%20entirely%20on%20raising%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20a%20wise%20strategy%20for%20any%20couple%20is%20the%20one%20that%20is%20agreed%20upon%20by%20both%20and%20that%20is%20applicable%20to%20the%20couple%20themselves%20and%20the%20circumstances%20they%20are%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenneth%20Tan%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20psychology%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Management%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20factors%20such%20as%20in-law%20support%2C%20finances%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20actual%20careers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20couples%20might%20want%20the%20'traditional'%20arrangement%2C%20whereas%20others%20do%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20not%20be%20prescriptive%20in%20a%20way%20where%20we%20merely%20follow%20social%20roles%20or%20follow%20how%20others%20have%20done%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20there%20is%20no%20wrong%20or%20right%20way%20to%20approach%20this%20matter%2C%20Leadingham%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BEvery%20family%20gets%20to%20create%20their%20own%20structure%20that%20works%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20communicating%2C%20partners%20need%20to%20listen%20to%20understand%20each%20other's%20point%20of%20view%20rather%20than%20defend%2C%20Leadingham%20said.%20And%20when%20dealing%20with%20conflict%2C%20creating%20an%20environment%20with%20a%20win-win%20solution%20for%20both%20people%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%2C%20it's%20not%20only%20love%20that%20keeps%20a%20couple%20together%2C%20it's%20how%20they%20fight%20and%20resolve%20their%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20it's%20about%20being%20a%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20these%20discussions%20should%20take%20place%20in%20a%20context%20where%20partners%20feel%20safe%20and%20secure%20in%20each%20other%2C%20and%20trust%20that%20the%20other%20is%20looking%20out%20for%20each%20other%20and%20that%20they%20are%20strong%20in%20their%20couplehood%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20marital%20couple%20that%20thinks%20in%20terms%20of%20'you'%20and%20'I%2C'%20instead%20of%20'we%2C'%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20committed%20in%20the%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-mendes-ryan-gosling-non-verbal-agreement-parenting-relationship-experts-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711596981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603afff16bde8d4ead27ca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-mendes-ryan-gosling-non-verbal-agreement-parenting-relationship-experts-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20way%20for%20couples%20to%20navigate%20childcare%20arrangements%20is%20to%20be%20open%20to%20discussion%20and%20make%20decisions%20on%20an%20equal%20standing%2C%20experts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-mendes-ryan-gosling-non-verbal-agreement-parenting-relationship-experts-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20China%20Discuss%20%26quot%3BComplete%20Disengagement%26quot%3B%20Along%20LAC%20In%20Fresh%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20