0in%20our%20home%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-2-bodies-recovered-from-submerged-pickup-truck-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711591084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6604c02b3f923f7dab01e965%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-2-bodies-recovered-from-submerged-pickup-truck-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20bodies%20recovered%20from%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Baltimore%20bridge%20collapse%20were%20inside%20a%20submerged%20red%20pickup%20truck%2C%20police%20said.%20Four%20men%20remain%20missing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A492%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-2-bodies-recovered-from-submerged-pickup-truck-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'In%20Satya%20we%20trust%E2%80%A6%20'%3A%20AI%20startup%20founder%20%E2%80%98jokes%E2%80%99%20about%20Microsoft%20CEO's%20influence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711590968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108834102%2Cimgsize-1104583.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fin-satya-we-trustai-startup-founder-jokes-about-microsoft-ceos-powerful-influence-in-tech-industry%2Farticleshow%2F108834102.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emad%20Mostaque%20jokes%20about%20Satya%20Nadella's%20AI%20impact%2C%20sparking%20speculation.%20Microsoft%20excels%20in%20AI%20with%20top%20talent%20and%20key%20partnerships.%20Nadella%20praised%20as%20a%20leading%20CEO%2C%20while%20Mostaque%20explores%20decentralized%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fin-satya-we-trustai-startup-founder-jokes-about-microsoft-ceos-powerful-influence-in-tech-industry%2Farticleshow%2F108834102.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAbsurd%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20Bureaucrats%20Slam%20Economist%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal's%20UPSC%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20bureaucrats%20on%20Wednesday%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bavoidable%26quot%3B%20the%20comments%20of%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20member%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20that%20five%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20preparation%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20exam%20by%20lakhs%20of%20students%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bwaste%20of%20youthful%20energy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20millions%20aspire%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20sought-after%20government%20services%20to%20contribute%20towards%20nation-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanyal%20has%20said%20that%20one%20should%20only%20attempt%20UPSC%20or%20other%20such%20examinations%20if%20one%20wants%20to%20become%20an%20administrator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20mentioned%2C%20it%20(is)%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20attempt%20the%20UPSC%20or%20other%20such%20exams%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20person%20wants%20to%20be%20an%20administrator.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20lakhs%20of%20people%20are%20spending%205-8%20years%20repeatedly%20doing%20this%20exam%20as%20a%20'way%20of%20life'.%20This%20is%20such%20a%20waste%20of%20youthful%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20comments%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20G%20Sundaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20absurd.%20India%20is%20a%20vast%20country.%20We%20are%20interested%20in%20a%20united%20India%20and%20that%20is%20why%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%2C%20(the%20first%20home%20minister%20of%20Independent%20India)%20created%20these%20services%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%2C%20among%20others.%20It%20is%20all%20working%20well.%26quot%3B%20There%20may%20be%20certain%20deficiencies%20which%20can%20of%20course%20be%20rectified%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESundaram%2C%20a%201962-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Gujarat%20cadre%2C%20who%20superannuated%20as%20the%20Tourism%20Secretary%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20(Sanyal's)%20comments%20were%20completely%20avoidable.%26quot%3B%20The%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20conducts%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%20every%20year%20in%20three%20stages%20--%20preliminary%2C%20main%20and%20personality%20test%20(interview)%20--%20to%20select%20officers%20for%20different%20central%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20K%20Sarkar%2C%20former%20secretary%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%2C%20said%20Sanyal's%20assertion%20was%20avoidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20waste%20of%20youthful%20energy%20or%20resources.%20I%20don't%20agree%20with%20his%20assertion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%201979-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20West%20Bengal%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20aspire%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20government%20services.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20best%20services%20in%20India%20to%20contribute%20towards%20nation-building%20and%20development.%20His%20comments%20were%20avoidable.%26quot%3B%20Former%20IAS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chopra%20said%20Sanyal%20is%20entitled%20to%20his%20views%20but%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20youths%20who%20wish%20to%20be%20civil%20servants%20is%20not%20in%20good%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20aspires%20to%20be%20an%20Ambani.%20People%20also%20want%20to%20be%20poets%2C%20painters%20and%20thespians.%20Many%20want%20to%20work%20for%20the%20government.%20And%20in%20the%20government%20there%20is%20no%20job%20more%20fulfilling%20than%20a%20district%20assignment%2C%20or%20a%20posting%20as%20a%20JS%20(joint%20secretary)%20in%20which%20you%20cover%20the%20entire%20domain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanyal%20is%20of%20course%20entitled%20to%20his%20views%2C%20but%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20young%20women%20and%20men%20who%20wish%20to%20be%20civil%20servants%20is%20not%20in%20good%20taste%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chopra%2C%20a%201985-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20Director%20of%20Mussoorie-based%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20of%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20--%20the%20country's%20premier%20training%20institute%20for%20civil%20servants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20bureaucrat%2C%20Kiran%20Puri%2C%20said%20preparing%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20waste%20of%20youthful%20energy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20are%20academically%20strong%20and%20knowledgeable%2C%20they%20only%20join%20the%20civil%20services.%20Civil%20servants%20are%20needed%20to%20run%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%201983-batch%20Central%20Secretariat%20Service%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20talented%20people%20do%20not%20devote%20their%20energy%20and%20attention%20towards%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20then%20how%20will%20the%20nation's%20development%20be%20ensured%2C%20she%20posed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20the%20best%20of%20minds%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20country%20and%20to%20ensure%20further%20ease%20of%20governance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Puri%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Joint%20Secretary%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Administrative%20Reforms%20and%20Public%20Grievances%20under%20the%20Union%20Personnel%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20S%20Y%20Quraishi%2C%20however%2C%20partially%20agreed%20with%20Sanyal's%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20partially%20right.%20Young%20people%20are%20putting%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20years%20preparing%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%20Some%20people%20leave%20lucrative%20jobs%20and%20hefty%20salaries%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20these%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuraishi%2C%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%2C%20suggested%20limiting%20the%20number%20of%20attempts%20being%20provided%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20too%20many%20attempts%20being%20provided%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%20It%20can%20be%20limited%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20three%20attempts%20as%20it%20was%20earlier.%20There%20may%20be%20some%20extra%20attempts%20for%20people%20belonging%20to%20scheduled%20caste%2C%20scheduled%20tribe%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServing%20IPS%20officer%20Pankaj%20Chaudhary%20also%20disagreed%20with%20Sanyal's%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCivil%20services%20exam%20and%20the%20UPSC%20act%20as%20the%20role%20model%20for%20many%20youngsters.%20These%20comments%20were%20completely%20avoidable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%202009-batch%20IPS%20officer%20of%20Rajasthan%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20civil%20services%20examination%20is%20transparent%20and%20provides%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20topper%20of%20Hindi%20in%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%20in%202008.%20A%20person%20like%20me%20from%20a%20Hindi%20background%20could%20become%20a%20part%20of%20this%20service%20as%20the%20UPSC%20and%20civil%20services%20examination%20shows%20it%20is%20very%20credible%20and%20unbiased%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20is%20Superintendent%20of%20Community%20Policing%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20thi