20Their%20business%20has%20been%20soaring%20with%20success%2C%20selling%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20worth%20of%20products%20every%20day.%20Their%20farm%20produces%2040%20tonnes%20of%20mushrooms%20and%2045%20tonnes%20of%20vegetables%20every%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20about%20how%20they%20do%20it%3F%20Here%20is%20what%20they%20have%20to%20say%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20our%20father%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20come%20true%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Ayush%20(25)%20and%20Rishabh%20(27)%20grew%20up%20watching%20their%20father%20dream%20of%20pursuing%20polyhouse%20farming.%20The%20family%20moved%20to%20Agra%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolyhouse%20farming%2C%20also%20referred%20to%20as%20greenhouse%20farming%20or%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20involves%20growing%20crops%20within%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20Polyhouses%2C%20constructed%20from%20transparent%20materials%20like%20polyethene%20or%20polycarbonate%2C%20permit%20sunlight%20penetration%20while%20trapping%20heat%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20working%20and%20could%20not%20dedicate%20full%20attention%20to%20it.%20He%20suggested%20my%20grandfather%20take%20it%20up%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20either.%20So%2C%20he%20always%20harboured%20this%20wish%2C%20and%20when%20my%20brother%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20it%2C%20we%20knew%20where%20to%20start%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ayush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20was%20in%20London%20studying%20BBA%2C%20and%20my%20brother%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296139%2Ftamil-nadu-man-quits-dubai-job-to-revive-water-bodies-help-lakhs-after-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudying%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20coming%20back%20home%20that%20year%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20return%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20Gupta%2C%20founders%20of%20A33%20Mushroom%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAyush%20and%20Rishabh%20Gupta%2C%20founders%20of%20A33%20Mushroom%20Farms.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20my%20brother%20was%20stuck%20in%20Dubai%20due%20to%20travel%20restrictions.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20time%20that%20he%20started%20feeling%20lonely%20and%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%20home.%20He%20realised%20that%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20near%20his%20family.%20So%2C%20during%20our%20conversations%2C%20he%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20return%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340041%2Fentrepreneur-save-family-business-harshit-tanay-agrawal-pistabarfi-cloud-kitchen-janta-dairy-sweets-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20brothers%20reunited%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20back%20to%20either%20London%20or%20Dubai%20and%20instead%20stay%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20always%20discuss%20how%2C%20if%20we%20ever%20became%20business%20persons%2C%20we%20would%20enter%20the%20food%20industry.%20However%2C%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20passion%20towards%20having%20a%20farm%20motivated%20us%20to%20try%20our%20hand%20at%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20brothers%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320228%2Fpune-brothers-quit-job-to-start-organic-farming-venture-worth-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20well-received%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Indian%20households%20for%20the%20relatives%20to%20have%20strong%20opinions.%20My%20father%20was%20told%20that%20he%20has%20put%20so%20much%20money%20into%20our%20education%20and%20sent%20us%20abroad%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisheartened%20by%20the%20reaction%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%20that%20gave%20them%20the%20courage.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20us%20that%20we%20need%20not%20listen%20to%20anyone.%20If%20this%20feels%20right%2C%20then%20we%20must%20continue%20with%20the%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20nod%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20the%20brother%20duo%20decided%20to%20use%20some%20savings%20and%20loan%20some%20amount%20to%20set%20up%20the%20polyhouse%20farm%20in%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%2C%20natural%20and%20fresh%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20the%20duo%20had%20initiated%20the%20setup%20of%20their%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20secured%20a%2040%20percent%20government%20subsidy%2C%20prompting%20us%20to%20commence%20with%20planting%20English%20Cucumber%20in%20our%20polyhouse%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20four%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20established%20their%20initial%20cultivation%20and%20harvested%20it%20within%20five%20months.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cucumber%20marked%20just%20the%20beginning.%20We%20sought%20further%20expansion%20and%20ventured%20into%20experimenting%20with%20additional%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Ayush%20recalls%2C%20while%20he%20was%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20small%20mushroom%20business.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sourced%20mushrooms%20from%20farmers%2C%20packed%20them%2C%20and%20sold%20them.%20Although%20brief%2C%20it%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20substantial%20profit%20potential%20of%20mushrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20was%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20father's%20wish%20to%20start%20a%20polyhouse%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20father%E2%80%99s%20wish%20to%20start%20a%20polyhouse%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20when%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20decided%20to%20diversify%20into%20mushrooms%2C%20they%20anticipated%20increased%20profits.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20allocate%201%20acre%20of%20the%20farm%20for%20other%20veggies%20such%20as%20cucumber%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20potatoes%2C%20and%202%20acres%20for%20mushrooms.%20We%20initiated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343926%2Feco-friendly-thermocol-kinoko-biotech-chaitanya-dubey-iit-kanpur-startup-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20and%20our%20profits%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20since%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20previous%20mushroom%20experience%2C%20Ayush%20also%20observed%20a%20trend%20in%20his%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20region%20is%20predominantly%20inhabited%20by%20vegetarians%20who%20favour%20mushrooms.%20Button%20mushroom%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20has%20surged%20over%20the%20years.%20With%20new%20recipes%20circulating%20online%2C%20people%20are%20relishing%20this%20chewy%20fungus.%20I%20even%20noticed%20mushrooms%20featuring%20prominently%20in%20wedding%20celebrations%2C%20with%20various%20dishes%20showcasing%20them%20as%20the%20main%20ingredient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20they%20yield%20approximately%2040%20tonnes%20of%20mushrooms%20per%20month.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20all%20A-grade%20mushrooms%2C%20distinguished%20by%20their%20maturity%2C%20well-formed%20shape%2C%20and%20meticulous%20trimming.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20are%20%E2%80%98B%E2%80%99%20grade%20mushrooms%2C%20which%2C%20due%20to%20irregular%20shapes%2C%20are%20sold%20to%20food%20processing%20companies%20for%20canning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperating%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Gupta%20Organic%20Farms%20and%20A3R%20Mushroom%20Farms%2C%20the%20b