agram.com%2Fletsliveivory%3Figsh%3DOGQ5ZDc2ODk2ZA%253D%253D%26utm_source%3Dqr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20close%20to%2050%20different%20games%20with%20different%20levels%20of%20difficulty%20that%20will%20also%20be%20live%20on%20our%20app.%20These%20test%20different%20skills%2C%20such%20as%20auditory%20skills%2C%20hand-eye%20coordination%2C%20visual%20reasoning%2C%20focus%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20short-term%20memory%2C%20among%2023%20different%20skills.%20The%20app%20is%20currently%20in%20its%20beta%20version%20slated%20for%20further%20testing%20but%20contains%20various%20games%20%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20we%20have%20a%20game%20which%20tests%20processing%20speed%2C%20estimation%2C%20and%20spatial%20perception.%20Apart%20from%20these%20cognitive%20games%2C%20Ivory%20also%20has%20a%20gamified%20quizzing%20experience%20in%20version%201%20across%20topics%20of%20interest%20for%20our%20target%20group%20(TG)%20apart%20from%20ongoing%20brain-teasers%20that%20we%20will%20soon%20drop%20on%20the%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jwala%20Narayanan%2C%20a%20consulting%20neuropsychologist%20at%20Annaswamy%20Mudaliar%20Hospital%20and%20Manipal%20Hospital%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20understand%20that%20dementia%20risks%20are%20diverse%2C%20making%20prevention%20a%20crucial%20strategy%20in%20the%20battle%20against%20it.%20Given%20the%20considerable%20challenges%20of%20behaviour%20change%2C%20Ivory%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20healthcare%20ecosystem%20becomes%20essential%2C%20harnessing%20technology%E2%80%99s%20advantages%20to%20inspire%20a%20positive%20shift%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20habits%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%2