s%20of%20New%20Jersey%20are%20bustling%20%E2%80%94%20office%20goers%20rushing%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20skip%20the%20traffic%20jam%2C%20the%20consistent%20hum%20drum%20of%20buses%2C%20the%20chatter%20of%20school%20kids%2C%20regular%20joggers%20trying%20to%20cram%20in%20those%20few%20extra%20minutes%20before%20the%20day%20begins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterspersed%20in%20these%20moments%20of%20hustle%20is%20the%20smell%20of%20coffee%20wafting%20from%20the%20cafes%20that%20line%20the%20sidewalk%2C%20the%20aroma%20acting%20like%20a%20beacon%20that%20draws%20to%20it%20all%20the%20above.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeenly%20watching%20this%20whole%20scene%20unfold%20is%20a%20woman.%20Her%20%3Cem%3Edesi%3C%2Fem%3E%20attire%20is%20suggestive%20of%20her%20origins.%20Her%20gaze%20is%20unwavering%20as%20she%20watches%20the%20cacophony%20of%20the%20northeastern%20US%20state.%20One%20might%20say%20her%20position%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20vibrant%20pink%20food%20truck%20is%20strategic%2C%20considering%20the%20view%20of%20400%20Central%20Ave%2C%20Jersey%20City%20she%20has%20from%20there.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20pink%20doors%20beside%20her%20illustration%2C%20magic%20is%20steamed%20(and%20fried)%20every%20day%20by%20a%20duo%20of%20Indian%20origin.%20The%20variety%20of%20momos%20whipped%20up%20in%20the%20food%20truck%20borrow%20their%20taste%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343137%2Fbengaluru-rameshwaram-cafe-started-by-iim-grad-divya-raghav-rao-podi-masala-dosa-idli-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20fusion%20flavours%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Ankita%20Nagpal%20%E2%80%94-%20one%20half%20of%20the%20duo%20that%20helms%20the%20%E2%80%98Fomo%20Momo%E2%80%99%20venture%20%E2%80%94%20feasted%20on%20when%20she%20was%20a%20child%20growing%20up%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20business%20partner%20and%20friend%2C%20Impreet%20Sodhi%2C%20and%20s