e%20than%20the%20average%20scooter%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20the%20largest%20floor%20board%20since%20people%20utilise%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20You%20will%20often%20see%20grocery%20bags%2C%20school%20bags%2C%20and%20even%20kids%20standing%20on%20them.%20So%20in%20our%20product%2C%20we%20have%20included%20%E2%80%98Lock%20and%20Load%20Pannier%20Mounts%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20are%20sturdy%20alloy%20mounts%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20scooter.%20Attach%20pannier%20boxes%2C%20load%20up%20and%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20the%20hustle%20culture%20of%20our%20youth%20and%20we%20have%20made%20a%20vehicle%20designed%20especially%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20also%20has%20a%2012-litre%20lockable%20glove%20box%20with%20a%20USB%20charger.%20%E2%80%9CStore%20and%20lock%20up%20your%20valuables%20for%20safety%2C%20and%20easily%20access%20them%20while%20being%20seated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20range%20anxiety%20that%20most%20people%20deal%20with%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scooters%20are%20usually%20used%20by%20Indians%20to%20drive%20within%20the%20cities%20and%20inter-city%20usage%20is%20usually%20via%20a%20motorcycle.%20Designed%20specifically%20for%20inter-city%20travel%2C%20we%20have%20offered%20a%20range%20of%20120%20km%20when%20fully-charged.%20So%20this%20way%2C%20a%20customer%20will%20be%20charging%20the%20vehicle%20once%20every%20three%20to%20four%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3P2LIUrMz5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3P2LIUrMz5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm